dct_description_sm: Map showing coastline of Cape Natal and the city of Durban; relief shown by hachures and soundings. Map includes profiles: Coast between the Umlass and Uncomass Rivers -- Mouth of Umlass R. -- C. Natal (bluff) N.E.b.E. -- Cape Natal (bluff) flagstaff -- Bar -- Sandy Point -- Blockhouse W.S.W. -- Sandy Point marks -- Bluff marks (white). At head of title: Africa, south east coast.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; sold by J.D. Potter, agent for the Admiralty charts ... , August 23rd, 1856.
